>Oku kuzakudwelisa itemplates zobeko lwephepha ezikhoyo kwindlela yakho.</emphasis
></para>

<para
>Inqwanqwa 2: Ngoku khetha <guilabel
>Ubeko Olucacileyo</guilabel
> icon ngoku nqakraza kanye ngeqhosha lasekhohlo le mouse yakho.</para>

