<para
><emphasis
>Le yitemplate esizakuyisebenzisa kufundiso</emphasis
></para>

<para
>Inqwanqwa 3: Ngoku qinisekisa ukhetho lwakho ngokunqakraza kwi <guibutton
>KULUNGILE</guibutton
> </para>

<mediaobject
