>&kword; izakuvula uxwebhu olutsha ngezakhelo ezintathu. Izakhelo zigqatyaziwe kwisiqalo esimhlophe, njengebhokisi ezingwevu. Ibhokisi nganye sisakhelo esahlukileyo.</emphasis
></para>

</sect1>

<sect1 id="tutorial-frame-select">
<title
>Ufundiso: Ikhetha isakhelo kwaye ingenisa okubhaliweyo kweso sakhelo</title>

<para
><emphasis
>Ukuqala ukungenisa okubhaliweyo (okanye ukudibanisa naluphi udidi lwedata lwalo nto), kuxwebhu, kufuneka kuqala uvemele icomputer yazi ukuba sesiphi isakhelo sokubeka idata kuso.</emphasis
></para>

<para
>Inqwanqwa 4: Beka isalathiso se mouse ngapha kwesakhelo esiphezulu-ekhohlo</para>
<para
>Inqwanqwa 5: Nqakraza kanye ngeqhosha lemouse ekhohlo.</para>

<mediaobject
><imageobject
><imagedata format="PNG" fileref="Tut4.png"/></imageobject
> <textobject
><phrase
>Udubulo lwekhusi</phrase
></textobject
></mediaobject>

<para
><emphasis
>Oku kukhetha isakhelo. Ungaxela ukuba oku sisakhelo sangoku kuba isalathisi sivela kwikona ephezulu ekhohlo. </emphasis
></para>

<para
>Inqwanqwa 6: Ngenisa okubhaliweyo okulandelayo kwibhodi yezitshixo: <userinput
>KWord Cinezela Ukhupho</userinput
>.</para>
<para
><mediaobject
