<para
><emphasis
>Oku yisampuli yokubhaliweyo yeleta yakho yendaba.</emphasis
></para>

<para
>Inqwanqwa 7: Khetha <emphasis
>KWord Cinezela Ukhupho</emphasis
> ngokubeka iosalathiso se mouse ekhohlo kwisiphelo sokubhaliweyo. Nqakraza kanye nge <mousebutton
>ekhohlo</mousebutton
> iqhosha le mouse kwaye utsale isalathiso se mouse ekunene. Okubhaliweyo okukhethiweyo kuzakubamhlophe kwisiqalo esimnyama.</para>

