<sect1 id="tutorial-resize-frame"
> <title
>Ufundiso: Itshintsha ubungakannai besakhelo</title>

<para
><emphasis
>Ngoku singenise okubhaliweyo, singabona ukuba isakhelo sikhulu kakhulu kokubhaliweyo. </emphasis
></para>

<para
>Inqwanqwa 9: Beka isalathiso se mouse ngapha komda wesakhelo, kwaye nqakraza kanye.</para>

<para
><emphasis
>Oku kuzakukhetha esi sakhelo, ngoko inokumiliswa-kwakhona.</emphasis
></para>

<para
><emphasis
>Uzakuqaphela ngoku isakhelo ukuba siiphawulwe mnyama, ngosikweri abasibozo abamnyama kugqabazo. Aba xande basetyenziswa ukulinganisela-kwakhona isakhelo.</emphasis
></para>

<para
>Inqwanqwa 10: Beka isalathiso se mouse ngapha kwesikweri esimnyama kwikona esezantsi ekunene yesakhelo. Nqakraza ngeqhosha le mouse ekhohlo kwaye yibambe phantsi. Tsala imouse phezulu kwaye nasekhohlo.</para>

<para
><mediaobject
><imageobject
><imagedata format="PNG" fileref="Tut11a.png"/></imageobject
> <textobject
><phrase
>Udubulo lwekhusi</phrase
></textobject
></mediaobject
></para>

<para
><emphasis
>Qaphela indlela isakhelo esitshintsha ngayo imilo. Nyenyisa ubungakanani nemilo yesakhelo ide ijongeke njengale:</emphasis
></para>

<para
><mediaobject
><imageobject
><imagedata format="PNG" fileref="Tut11b.png"/></imageobject
> <textobject
><phrase
>Udubulo lwekhusi</phrase
></textobject
></mediaobject
></para>

<para
>Xa isenza, khupha iqhosha le mouse.</para>

</sect1>

<sect1 id="tutorial-move-frame"
> 
<title
>Ufundiso: Ukusa isakhelo kwiphepha</title>

<para
>Ngoku senze ibloko encinane, sizakuyibeka embindini phezulu kwephepha.</para>

<para
>Inqwanqwa 11: Beka isalathisi se mouse ngapha komda wesakhelo (kodwa hayi nakweziphi izikweri ezimnyama).</para>

<para
><emphasis
>Isalathisi sizakutshintsha ngoku kwindlela ezine zetolo. Oku kwalatha &kword; sele ilungele ukusa isakhelo kwiphepha.</emphasis
></para>

<para
>Inqwanqwa 12: Nqakraza kwaye ubambe ngeqhosha lasekhohlo le mouse. Tsala imouse, kwaye isakhelo sizakuyilandela. Beka isakhelo embindini wephepha kufutshane ngentla. Xa ukholwa ngendawo yayo uyokugqibela, khupha iqhosha le mouse.</para>

