>Isalathisi sitshintshele kwinwele-ezingaphaya. Ungazoba ibhokisi yokubhaliweyo kwakho okutsha ngesi salathiso. Qala ngokubeka isalathiso kwikona enye. Nqakraza kwaye bamba i <mousebutton
>ekhohlo</mousebutton
> iqhosha le mouse. Tsala imouse kwikonw ngekona. Ugqabazo luzakuvela olumele isakhelo sokubhaliweyo esitsha. Xa unesakhelo sokubhaliweyo sobungakanani obububo, khupha i <mousebutton
