<sect1 id="tutorial-summary">
<title
>Ufundiso: Isishwankathelo</title>

<para
>Ngethemba olu fundiso lukwazise kondoqo bokusebenzisa izakhelo kwi &kword;.</para>

<para
>Kule ncopho, waziswe kuyo:</para>

<itemizedlist
> <listitem
><para
>Idibanisa okubhaliweyo kwisakhelo.</para
></listitem
> <listitem
><para
>Iyenza, iyasa, iyalinganisela kwakhona kwaye icima izakhelo.</para
></listitem
> <listitem
><para
>kwaye ilinganisela kwakhona okubhaliweyo.</para
></listitem
> </itemizedlist>
<para
>Ngoku uzakuqala ukuva khululeke kakhulu ngondoqo be &kword;.</para>
</sect1>
